rows.label: qev087101_MSG0002
rows.name: Well, it isn't every day the director general stops by for a visit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0003
rows.name: I'm a busy man, I fear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0004
rows.name: But something's come up that I'd like your team to handle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0005
rows.name:
Stuffy suit came to the right place.
Make request and Tatsu will see what he can do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0006
rows.name:
...Right. Well, I'd like to propose we enhance
our surveillance of the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0007
rows.name: Is there something you're expecting to find?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0008
rows.name: We've had a string of unusual reports lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0009
rows.name:
There have been rumors that the Ganglion
are fighting amongst themselves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0010_2
rows.name:
With all those species working together,
I imagine they've no shortage of infighting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0011
rows.name:
Which is precisely what we want to exploitâ€”
hence the need for intel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0012
rows.name:
And why I'd like you to focus on
expanding FrontierNav for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087101_MSG0013
rows.name: All right. We'll take it on as a formal request from you.[ST:wait ]
